Poppe Tyson in New York, a unit of Bozell, Jacobs, Kenyon & Eckhardt, has acquired Animated Systems and Designs Inc., a provider of interactive new media in Palo Alto, Calif. Terms were not disclosed. Rae B. Callender, 34, president of Animated, will continue in that position, supervising 41 employees who work for clients like the International Business Machines Corporation and the Microsoft Corporation. Animated will operate independently, working on new business in conjunction with Poppe Tyson.